breakpoint         class infix      dimensions
extra small                           < 576px
small                  sm            >= 576px
medium                 md            >= 768px
large                  lg            >= 992px
extra large            xl            >= 1200px
extra extra large      xxl           >= 1400px

# default breakpoint is xxs for bootstrap rules

